I have made this several times and it has been a hit at each party. It is delightfully different. And spicy - beware if you have Watermelon Purists...I usually prepare a small bowl of plain, cubed watermelon for those who cannot tolerate spicy foods.

Rating: 1
I love both watermelon and cilantro, but the spices hide the taste of both. It's potentially a way to use a flavorless watermelon that you would otherwise toss...and effectively hides the cilantro taste for your friends who don't care for it. Not a keeper for me or my family.

