Rating: 3
I found this recipe while looking for a watermelon salsa recipe. It's similar to watermelon salsa and is very unusual, easy and tasty. It is great with BBQ chicken. I will definitely make it again, and look forward to trying it with basil.

Rating: 3
I first made this when it appeared in June '93. Maybe the unusual combination of ingredients has kept others from trying it. The first time I used basil; the second time, cilantro. Delicious both times. A great way to use watermelon that's not sweet enough to have for dessert. Just add a little sugar to the seasonings.